# Link Checker Exclusions
# Domains and patterns to exclude from link checking to avoid false positives

# Social media (rate-limited)
https://twitter.com/*
https://t.co/*
https://x.com/*
https://facebook.com/*
https://linkedin.com/*
https://instagram.com/*

# CDNs and external resources
https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/*
https://unpkg.com/*
https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/*

# Analytics and tracking
https://www.google-analytics.com/*
https://analytics.google.com/*

# Comment systems
https://disqus.com/*

# Localhost and development
http://localhost*
http://127.0.0.1*

# Mail links
mailto:*
